Once you have experienced working at Awfis, it will change the way you think about collaborative working.

Housed within the magnificent Aston Building, this centre appeals to fast growing businesses for its locality and premium nature of the property. In the same lane as renowned production houses and one of the most popular locality in Western Mumbai."
